narratives.question_text: Were the resources available to you - library, fabrication labs, classroom, software, desk space, etc. adequate for the fulfillment of the assigned work?  If not, please make suggestions.
comments: Having all of the relevant books for the class placed on Open Reserve in the library is a bad idea because the students can't actually check out books. We are only able to look at the books in the library and its really hard to write a paper down their with our computers being upstairs.
